                      <p className="font-medium">ðŸ¤– ML: Naive Bayes (Google Colab)</p>
                      <p>ðŸ“Š Dataset: 79,540 Kaggle EHR samples</p>
                      <div className="flex gap-2 justify-center mt-1">
